description:
Template for creating a Single Page App (SPA) with Angular and ASP.NET Core following the Clean Architecture principles.

      Technologies:
      - ASP.NET Core 5
      - Entity Framework Core 5
      - Angular 10
      - MediatR
      - NSwag
      - AutoMapper
      - FluentValidation
      - NUnit, FluentAssertions, Moq and Respawn
      - Docker
      - Microsoft.Extensions.Diagnostics.HealthChecks
      - SpecFlow
      - Bogus
